Show HN: I built vanishdb.com which lets you create a sandbox DB with one click
text:
I built vanishdb.com which lets you create a sandbox DB with one click.

Supports MySQL 8.0 right now.

Databases are removed after 30 days of inactivity.

Feedback welcome.
